{"tid":2253929,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"解放軍沙頭角靶場疑射TG 刺鼻氣味襲小坑新村","createTime":"2020-10-22T13:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T14:00:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0398b438a8bacee8d19d1a4218d1832235df0079","tid":2253929,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:11:31.000Z","msg":"解放軍沙頭角路新圍軍營的練靶場，今午進行訓練時疑發射催淚彈，刺鼻的催淚氣體隨風飄至鄰近的小坑新村，令村民非常不適難受，警方發言人則表示暫時未收到類似報案。<br />\n<br />\n小坑新村原居民何女士表示，練靶場差不多每日都有訓練，經常聽到真槍實彈的「砰砰」聲，但亦未算嚴重影響村民生活。不過，今日下午2時許，何女士突然嗅到刺鼻的氣味，非常難受，過去未曾遇過，但第一時間已想到與解放軍訓練有關。<br />\n<br />\n何女士往練靶場方向查看，隨即看到有白煙在練靶場冒出，而且白煙並無快速消散，並會沉在地面一段長時間，「我唔肯定係催淚彈，我未聞過，但啲煙好刺鼻，而且佢係幾支煙射上天，跟住跌落哋再冒煙」。何女士稱，刺鼻氣體由下午2時開始，至傍晚6時仍斷斷續續傳出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201022/IZSYXCZC4RH4RMJE6AX4ABQA5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201022%2FIZSYXCZC4RH4RMJE6AX4ABQA5Q%2F&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPV9PyQTEnBXXUT3Ba6PvfAw%3D&h=8ae9fac5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201022%2FIZSYXCZC4RH4RMJE6AX4ABQA5Q%2F&h=cc51fab9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201022/IZSYXCZC4RH4RMJE6AX4ABQA5Q/</a>"},{"pid":"7e7798f4903fcad2ba8bfe82190ee767112b4ea2","tid":2253929,"uid":76804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:12:28.000Z","msg":"咁撚鐘意射tg就番屋企吸胡椒粉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f945da72c26ba1eb49234c6dfc095ac74dfb4e4","tid":2253929,"uid":191661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:13:02.000Z","msg":"污染地球<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ccd0b166c52acd30aade6605e964fd4170398da","tid":2253929,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T13:13:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3a86d2688212982d621d2ca38aae4e864ce28a8","tid":2253929,"uid":38904,"like":1,"d